+### 1. Operator Reconciliation Failure
+**Symptom:** `VDISession` created but no Pod/Service/Ingress appears. Status remains `Pending`.
+**Root Cause:** Operator crashed, RBAC missing, or invalid Template.
+**Verification:**
+```bash
